IMAPAccount university
Host 127.0.0.1
Port 1143
UserCmd "get-pass email/psu email"
PassCmd "get-pass email/psu"
SSLType None
AuthMechs LOGIN

IMAPStore university-remote
Account university

MaildirStore university-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.local/share/mail/university/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/university/Inbox

Channel university
Far :university-remote:
Near :university-local:
SyncState *
Patterns * !Trash !Archive !Junk !"Social Activity Notifications" !"Conversation History" !"Unsent Messages" !"Sync Issues*"
Create Both
Sync All
Expunge Near


IMAPAccount personal
