MaildirStore personal-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.local/share/mail/personal/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/personal/Inbox

Channel personal
Far :personal-remote:
Near :personal-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
SyncState *
Sync All
Expunge Near
